{"tid":330583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ios 10.3.3出現大量明顯的 Bug","createTime":"2017-07-21T10:47:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T07:21:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5abaa83d344cbc5525277b4c81d1d1c64d85ee55","tid":330583,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:47:22.000Z","msg":"1 用戶無法清除 Safari 流覽器中的歷史記錄和網站數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2 橫屏 Bug 的表現為用戶在 iPhone 控制中心啟動&ldquo;豎排方向鎖定&rdquo;，然後開啟橫<br />\n   屏遊戲或應用，之後雙擊 Home 鍵，設備會出現卡屏問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3 設備鎖屏後 Wi-Fi 斷連，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4 iPhone 播放音樂時音量會自動變小<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5 備忘錄、提醒事項應用出現閃退的問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據國外用戶反映，iOS 10.3.3 中存在一個明顯的 Bug：用戶無法清除 Safari 流覽器中的歷史記錄和網站數據。該問題已經連續出現在 iOS 10 的 4 個版本中，蘋果支持社區收到數百個有關此問題的反饋。<br />\n<br />\n　　威鋒網友在升級 iOS 10.3.3 後也向我們反映了部分問題，首先談論最多的要數橫屏 Bug。橫屏 Bug 的表現為用戶在 iPhone 控制中心啟動&ldquo;豎排方向鎖定&rdquo;，然後開啟橫屏遊戲或應用，之後雙擊 Home 鍵，設備會出現卡屏問題。鋒友表示，iOS 10.0 發布以來就存在橫屏 Bug，iOS 10.3.3 顯然也沒修復這一問題。<br />\n<br />\n　　還有少數鋒友反映，在使用 iOS 10.3.3 過程中，出現設備鎖屏後 Wi-Fi 斷連，iPhone 播放音樂時音量會自動變小以及備忘錄、提醒事項應用出現閃退的問題。不知道升級了 iOS 10.3.3 的你有沒出現同樣的狀況？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.feng.com/iPhone/news/2017-07-21/IOS-10.3.3-Bug-but-still-worth-the-upgrade_686068.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.feng.com%2FiPhone%2Fnews%2F2017-07-21%2FIOS-10.3.3-Bug-but-still-worth-the-upgrade_686068.shtml&d=lQxHVXYVGApsbYdR3oXkxp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=38c99d47\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.feng.com/iPhone/news/2017-07-21/IOS-10.3.3-Bug-but-still-worth-the-upgrade_686068.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"3bc1547fd7539a056a21d69dc30753a984f6bd11","tid":330583,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"Apple已死"},{"pid":"6163f4626d24a9bae2fc382faabff58351a3e51f","tid":330583,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:53:08.000Z","msg":"提大家係時候換機啦"},{"pid":"308429042ec2e1b859700e5da2238447cf833bfc","tid":330583,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:56:16.000Z","msg":"1 用戶無法清除 Safari 流覽器中的歷史記錄和網站數據<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAll    AV, BT Record Keep Forever<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cae967c2d71cd9d3505df50391681147753aa51","tid":330583,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Apple已死</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但樓豬照買"},{"pid":"c43628142d9878cac72c54eb25af3324e771a627","tid":330583,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Apple已死</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但樓豬照買</blockquote><br />\n無辦法，An機仲多bug<br />\n<br />\n唯有期待大日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66257e4d2b3d277f3470a047a4e7ac601119ac01","tid":330583,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Apple已死</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但樓豬照買</blockquote><br />\n無辦法，An機仲多bug<br />\n<br />\n唯有期待大日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日本應該唔會浪費錢搞os了"},{"pid":"f5a0213b3c96a5e9459c9ba2d0ac9052c9f6b2d6","tid":330583,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:19:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1 用戶無法清除 Safari 流覽器中的歷史記錄和網站數據<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAll    AV, BT Record Kee